            </div>
            <div class="about-w3layouts-left col-lg-9 col-md-9 col-sm-9">
              <h6 class="mb-lg-3 mb-2">Travel</h6>
              <p>Let’s explore the world together</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row my-lg-5 my-md-4 my-3">
            <div class="about-w3layouts-left col-lg-9 col-md-9 col-sm-9">
